---
title: "End-to-End Data Flow: Rep Asks for Meeting Prep"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Rep as Sales Rep
    participant Slack as Slack
    participant Bolt as Bolt SDK
    participant Router as Router (Haiku)
    participant Coach as Coach (Claude Sonnet)
    participant RAG as RAG Pipeline (Voyage + Qdrant)
    participant HS as HubSpot MCP
    participant Web as Web Search MCP
    participant BQ as BigQuery MCP

    Rep->>Slack: /coach prep for QBR with Acme Corp
    Slack->>Bolt: slash_command event
    Bolt->>Router: Classify intent

    Router-->>Bolt: route = coach, workflow = prep

    Bolt->>Coach: Execute prep workflow

    par Parallel data gathering
        Coach->>HS: Get Acme Corp deals, contacts, recent notes
        HS-->>Coach: 3 open deals, 12 contacts, 8 recent notes
    and
        Coach->>RAG: Search QBR preparation + enterprise accounts
        RAG-->>Coach: QBR playbook section + enterprise best practices
    and
        Coach->>Web: Search Acme Corp latest news 2026
        Web-->>Coach: Recent funding round, new CTO hired
    and
        Coach->>BQ: SELECT win_rate, avg_deal_size FROM deals
        BQ-->>Coach: 67% win rate, $45K avg deal size
    end

    Coach->>Coach: Synthesize prep brief (Claude Sonnet 4.5)
    Coach-->>Bolt: Formatted prep brief

    Bolt->>Slack: Block Kit message with account summary, talking points, risk areas, agenda, news
    Slack->>Rep: Meeting prep brief in DM
